{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.elimTopPre\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">elimTopPre</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Reduce a `Prop`-lattice goal `(⊤ : Prop) ⊑ φ` to the bare proposition `φ` via `top_le_prop`,\nreturning any other goal unchanged. The match on `Sort 0` keeps it to the `Prop` base lattice,\nwhere the reduction is sound; entailments at an abstract lattice carrier pass through. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.elimTopPre","kind":"def","line":160,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.elimTopPre","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.lean#L160-L169"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.reduceTopAppliedPre?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">reduceTopAppliedPre?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">target </span><span class=\"fn\">pre</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">Meta.Sym.SymM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Reduce a precondition that is the bare top applied to the state arguments introduced by\n`le_of_forall_le`, `(⊤ : σ₁ → … → σₙ → Prop) s₁ … sₙ`, to the bare `(⊤ : Prop)`, rewriting `goal`'s\ntarget `pre ⊑ rhs` to `⊤ ⊑ rhs`. The equation `pre = ⊤` is built on demand by folding\n`Lean.Order.top_apply` over the excess arguments (mirroring `replaceEPostHeadBot?`'s `bot_apply`\nfold) and applied with `replaceTargetEq`.\n\nThe proof term is built directly with `mkApp`/`mkConst` and instances extracted from `pre`, avoiding\n`mkAppM`/instance synthesis (both expensive and unable to unify `max`-of-universe-variable instance\nlevels in the abstract-monad setting). Returns `none` if `pre` is not the bare top applied to ≥ 1\nargument, or its lattice instances are not in the expected `instCompleteLatticePi` shape (the caller\nthen falls through).\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.reduceTopAppliedPre?","kind":"def","line":105,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.reduceTopAppliedPre?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.lean#L105-L158"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.splitLatticeOp?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">splitLatticeOp?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">rhs</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Decompose a supported lattice connective (`⊓`, `⇨`, `⌜p⌝`, `⊤`) or a registered frame operator on the\nRHS of `pre ⊑ rhs` by saturating it with the built-in and `@[frameproc]` rewrites, closing it with a\nterminal, and point-framing any excess state arguments. Returns `none` if the head is neither a\nbuilt-in connective nor a frame operator, or its rule does not apply.\n\nAn embedded proposition `⌜p⌝` is decomposed only when the precondition is `⊤`: its `⊤`-fixed terminal\n`top_le_ofProp` fails to apply otherwise, since turning `pre ⊑ ⌜p⌝` into the subgoal `p` drops `pre`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.splitLatticeOp?","kind":"def","line":84,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.splitLatticeOp?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.lean#L84-L103"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.reduceEPostHead?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">reduceEPostHead?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">target </span><span class=\"fn\">α </span><span class=\"fn\">inst </span><span class=\"fn\">pre </span><span class=\"fn\">rhs</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Reduce an `EPost.Cons.head` projection on the RHS of `pre ⊑ rhs` to the underlying component:\nconcrete `epost⟨…⟩` values project to the selected component, and `⊥.head x₁ … xₙ` rewrites to\n`⊥` via `replaceEPostHeadBot?`. Returns `none` if the RHS is not such a projection.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.reduceEPostHead?","kind":"def","line":48,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.reduceEPostHead?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.lean#L48-L66"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.introPre\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">introPre</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">rule</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/Apply.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.BackwardRule\">Meta.Sym.BackwardRule</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> (<a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.FVarId\">FVarId</a>)</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Apply precondition-intro rule `rule` to `goal`, then introduce the freed hypothesis,\nleaving `⊤` as the residual precondition. Returns the new goal and the introduced hypothesis. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.introPre","kind":"def","line":38,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.introPre","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.lean#L38-L46"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.unfoldTriple\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">unfoldTriple</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Unfold `⦃P⦄ x ⦃Q; E⦄` into the underlying entailment `P ⊑ wp x Q E`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.unfoldTriple","kind":"def","line":32,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.unfoldTriple","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Entails.lean#L32-L36"}}],"imports":["Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Context","Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.EPost","Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.RuleCache","Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Util","Lean.Meta.Sym.InferType","Lean.Meta.Sym.InstantiateMVarsS","Lean.Meta.Sym.Util"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Entails"}